{"tid":1186538,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬會面巴西教練淚流滿面：我無強姦！","createTime":"2019-06-05T03:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T06:42:08.000Z","uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aaff5b17b291884c45e1d21cb615c1ed9424cf5f","tid":1186538,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"尼馬（Neymar）日前深陷「強姦」風波之中，在這樣的大背景下，尼馬和巴西教練蒂特（Bacchi）進行了一次會談，結果尼馬情緒失控，當場淚如雨下。<br />\n<br />\n  巴西《環球體育》透露，尼馬日前和巴西教練蒂特進行了一次長時間對話。當著蒂特的面，尼馬哭了，面對強姦指控，尼馬堅決否認，他說因為人們對他的誤解，使得他非常的疲累。<br />\n<br />\n  雖然深陷風波之中，尼馬還是要求正常參加訓練，因為他覺得和隊友在一起，能讓他的情緒好一些。<br />\n<br />\n  上週六，尼馬被指控涉嫌性侵，儘管尼馬此後通過社交網絡自證清白，但是檢方對其調查也已經開始。尼馬到底是真強姦，抑或是被「仙人跳」？這還需要警方的進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n  （小九）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daeed9fd906a4149ca1a932e453150e65d90db80","tid":1186538,"uid":81783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBvjcyV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBvjcyV.png&h=9308f177&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f1d1e85c14b08a39343851b7696e4a97aa714ed","tid":1186538,"uid":7916,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWjv3U0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWjv3U0.png&h=3cc65d38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"692aa68984f38f117c1e63a513ae4579cd8c610a","tid":1186538,"uid":21398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f1d1e85c14b08a39343851b7696e4a97aa714ed","tid":1186538,"uid":7916,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWjv3U0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWjv3U0.png&h=3cc65d38&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"屁馬：巴西教練！我好想屌閪呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class